{
  "fadein": 1.5,
  "scripts": [
    {
      "say": "航空战准备，舰载机队正在前往目标上空……嗯？",
      "actor": 207030,
      "side": 2,
      "bgm": "level-french2",
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "dir": 1
    },
    {
      "actor": 207030,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "黎塞留，阿尔及利亚一个人脱离了维希舰队，正在向我们的方向高速驶来。难道是来做战前谈判的…？"
    },
    {
      "say": "终于要来了么……很好。",
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 4
    },
    {
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "全员停火，不要攻击阿尔及利亚！我去和她谈谈。"
    },
    {
      "actor": 903020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#ffff4d",
      "flashin": {
        "alpha": [
          1,
          0
        ],
        "black": true,
        "delay": 0.5,
        "dur": 0.5
      },
      "say": "好久不见，黎塞留卿。没想到自从上次分别之后，我们会在这种场景下重逢啊。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "flashout": {
        "alpha": [
          0,
          1
        ],
        "black": true,
        "dur": 0.5
      }
    },
    {
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "嗯，真是好久不见了，阿尔及利亚。上次见面的时候------"
    },
    {
      "say": "阳光、青草、鲜花、和甜点。大家上一次像这样聚在一起还是在教廷花园的茶会中呢。",
      "actor": 903020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#ffff4d",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 2
    },
    {
      "say": "是啊，那次应该是大家在一起的最后一次茶会了。",
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 3
    },
    {
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "记得那时候倔强拉着鲁莽说要给大家表演魔法，结果准备好的“魔法用具”被沃克兰偷偷换掉了…"
    },
    {
      "say": "结果甜点没弄出来，反而弄出了一串五颜六色的爆炸。最后还是靠敦刻尔克赶来救火，带了一批新的甜点过来。",
      "actor": 903020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#ffff4d",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 2
    },
    {
      "say": "敦刻尔克……",
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 3
    },
    {
      "actor": 903020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#ffff4d",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "黎塞留卿不怀念那个味道么？甜甜的、软软的、仿佛将“甜美”这个词具象化一样的敦刻尔克的甜点。如果没有它们的话，茶会都会失去一层光彩呢。"
    },
    {
      "say": "…………",
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 2
    },
    {
      "say": "还有斯特拉斯堡、普罗旺斯、布列塔尼，让·巴尔…多亏了你的皇家盟友，这种时光已经不会再有了。",
      "actor": 903020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#ffff4d",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 2
    },
    {
      "say": "她们现在，都怎么样了……",
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 4
    },
    {
      "say": "敦刻尔克因为伤势过重一直停留在凯比尔港。至于让·巴尔她们…呵呵，已经连“遗骸”都被铁血夺走了。",
      "actor": 903020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#ffff4d",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 3
    },
    {
      "say": "如果你以后想去缅怀她们，只能跑去铁血的教堂了吧。前提是在铁血还能有代表信仰的教堂留存下来的话。",
      "actor": 903020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#ffff4d",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 2
    },
    {
      "say": "………………",
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 3
    },
    {
      "say": "听我说，阿尔及利亚，侵占了我们家园的铁血才是真正的敌人，我们没有像这样相互争斗的必要。",
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 4
    },
    {
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "我们的利刃应该用来保护同伴和祖国，而不是像现在这样指向彼此。"
    },
    {
      "say": "带领舰队加入我们吧，加入自由鸢尾。让我们为了祖国的同伴、未来与希望而战！",
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 1
    },
    {
      "say": "加入自由鸢尾，然后和那边的皇家舰队“和睦相处”么？真是个好建议，希望让凯比尔港，让卡萨布兰卡港的同伴们也听听。",
      "actor": 903020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#ffff4d",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 1
    },
    {
      "actor": 903020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#ffff4d",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "至于“相互争斗的必要”……"
    },
    {
      "say": "黎塞留，从你在危机时刻选择抛弃祖国而不是患难与共，从你在皇家背叛之后选择与她们继续狼狈为奸的时候。",
      "actor": 903020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#ffff4d",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 1
    },
    {
      "say": "我们会有现在像这样相互斗争的一天，就已经是定局了。",
      "actor": 903020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#ffff4d",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 1
    },
    {
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "……我对于皇家做过的事无可辩驳，也不打算辩驳。这是我们痛苦、但是必须经历的试炼。"
    },
    {
      "say": "你应该十分清楚，如果碧蓝航线真的靠得住，鸢尾教国当初就不会失守…要想守护教廷，从来就只能依靠我们自己。",
      "actor": 903020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#ffff4d",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 1
    },
    {
      "actor": 903020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#ffff4d",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "投降吧，黎塞留卿。鸢尾教国也好，维希教廷也好，不论名称如何变化，你应该效忠的祖国一直都在那里。"
    },
    {
      "say": "现在回归维希教廷，我可以用圣教骑士的名义发誓，教廷一定会对你既往不咎的。",
      "actor": 903020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#ffff4d",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 2
    },
    {
      "say": "枢机主教不应该站在教廷的对立面，你应该来领导我们，重新恢复昔日荣耀的鸢尾教国啊！",
      "actor": 903020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#ffff4d",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 1
    },
    {
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "…现在的维希教廷，只是铁血打着祖国的幌子收买人心，控制同胞的工具。我是不会效忠这样的教廷的。"
    },
    {
      "say": "只有在赶走铁血、推翻维希教廷，建立了正确的秩序之后，我们才能有恢复鸢尾教国昔日荣耀的可能性。",
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 2
    },
    {
      "say": "为此，我才成立了自由鸢尾。只有一个彻底摆脱铁血控制的鸢尾，才能真正团结到我们的力量。",
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 4
    },
    {
      "say": "而只有我们团结一切可以团结的力量，才能真正实现我们的目标。",
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 1
    },
    {
      "say": "……看来交涉决裂了呢。果然，我们之间的破碎的东西已经不是依靠简单的言语就能够弥合的了。",
      "actor": 903020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#ffff4d",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 3
    },
    {
      "say": "………我是不会放弃的。",
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 2
    },
    {
      "say": "我也不会放弃哦。不过看起来，首先我们要在战场上见了呢。",
      "actor": 903020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#ffff4d",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 2
    },
    {
      "say": "祝你武运昌隆，黎塞留卿。",
      "actor": 903020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#ff5c5c",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "expression": 1
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "「骑士」留下这句话后，转过身去，面向维希教廷舰队的方向，头也不回的离开了。"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "「主教」望着「骑士」远去的身影，轻轻叹了口气，也向着联合舰队的方向驶去了。"
    },
    {
      "say": "……敦刻尔克的甜点，真的再想吃一次啊。",
      "actor": 805010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
